Fresh ideas. Smart solutions. Local decisions.








Montecito Bank & Trust Business Banking
You know better than anyone that managing your business takes vision, creativity, and lots of hard work. It also takes a close, collaborative banking relationship that supports your company as it grows and evolves. The first step in building that kind of partnership is finding the right bank -- one with the stability, financial resources, and strong commitment to meet your current needs and future goals. Discover why MB&T is the choice of so many local nonprofits and small and large businesses.





