MB&T Secure Mail

Please use our Secure Mail service for sending emails to MB&T associates concerning personal or business banking matters, when confidential information is involved. This includes cases when we request you to send us documents or other financial information. Keeping your data safe is our top priority.



How to use MB&T Secure Mail




Open MB&T Secure Mail



Enter your email address when prompted, then click Continue.


Fill in the registration information (be sure to remember this password), then click Continue.


A verification email has been sent to your email address. Click the link in this email to activate your account.


After your account has been verified, click Continue.


When presented with the secure email form, enter the email adddress of the recipient in the "To" field (1). You can attach a file by clicking Attach a file (2), then click "Add+". After you finish your message, click Send (3).














