Learn more about Montecito Bank & Trust

          Montecito Bank & Trust was established March 1975. It holds assets of 1.33 billion US dollars. That makes it a regional bank that most likely covers their local population well. A point to consider when choosing a bank is it's health. This bank appears to be healthy. It has a texas ratio of 2%. Lower is better!
        
Looking for an alternative to Montecito Bank & Trust?

          If you're looking for higher interest rates and lower fees, but are willing to give up the "walk-in" experience of a local
          branch, you may want to browse our curated selection of best online banks.
        







