Montecito Bank & Trust Overview



Website:

www.montecito.com

Locations:


                                                             Santa Barbara, CA 

                                                
& 5 other cities



Employees:
305




Founded:
N/A
President:
Rodney Brown
Industry:

State Commercial Banks
& 1 other industry



Revenue:
$82,523,470





                                            A state commercial bank, Montecito Bank & Trust is located at Santa Barbara, CA. It pulls in a yearly revenue of $82.5 million and employs 305 people. Simply, Montecito Bank & Trust is making an undeniable splash in the boutique market. President Rodney Brown currently heads the company.
                                        









