Time at Montecito Bank & Trust

























                                                Employees hail from a wide variety of alma maters, but the most common are Westmont College, Loyola Law School of Los Angeles, Foothill High school , Smith College, and Santa Barbara City College.
                                            

                                                For a closer look at the intellectual environment at Montecito Bank & Trust, look at the educational trends among employees. Employees at Montecito Bank & Trust typically hold a J.D., Bachelor of Arts - Double Major, High School Diploma, Bachelor of Arts, and Pharmacy Technician License  degrees.
                                            

